data.description: Welcome to the perfect family home located in Sec. 15! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom property with a 2-car garage offers nearly 3000 square feet of comfortable living space. With high ceilings and a split floor plan, this house is both spacious and functional.  With a brand new roof installed in 2023 and a pristine pool added in 2017 (with screens being replaced in two weeks), this house is ready to become your forever home.  Inside, you'll find a well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops and a large island, making meal preparation a breeze. The open living area is ideal for family gatherings or entertaining friends. The four bedrooms provide ample space for a growing family or guests, and one of them can easily be converted into a home office or playroom.  This home's location is a significant advantage, with close proximity to shopping, dining, and medical facilities. Plus, the easy interstate access ensures you can reach Fort Myers or Sarasota with ease.
